      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents, noticeable rust spots on the wheel arches, and heavy paint oxidation throughout. Inside, the upholstery has multiple tears and the headliner is beginning to sag. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention for a persistent oil leak and a noisy suspension. This would be an ideal project car for someone mechanically inclined or a very basic budget option for short-distance travel.",
