      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that qualifies as showroom-original. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its factory-fresh tactile integrity. Mechanically, the automobile performs with the absolute precision and refinement expected of a masterfully preserved unit. For the discerning client who demands a vehicle in peerless condition, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar of the highest caliber.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
